        "content": "## SNMP Monitoring Not Yet Configured\n\nSNMP scraping for switches and APs is deferred. To enable:\n\n1. Generate SNMP exporter config: see [snmp_exporter generator](https://github.com/prometheus/snmp_exporter/tree/main/generator)\n2. Re-enable `services.prometheus.exporters.snmp` in `exporters.nix`\n3. Add scrape jobs to `prometheus.nix` targeting Firewalla and OUI switches\n\nCurrent SNMP exporter port: 9116 (pre-allocated in firewall rules).",
